This particular report was built using the default settings that get applied when initially creating an Analysis Report. It violates a number of accessibility design requirements. The Dashboard Prompts above are also problematic for users with accessibility needs. [br/]
[br/]
These violations [i][b]can be[/b][/i] corrected by simple property changes. However, the content developer must know about the requirements for proper accessible design and how to correct these issues when building content within the Analysis Editor.[br/]
